data.text:
Re: Locker Room #19: Danny/Carmine--Everyone's Favorite Danny-in-Distr

Apparently Carmine and Vanessa are not actually married yet. In an interview with a saop magazine Vanessa says what everyone thinks was their wedding was just a pre wedding party, they are actually getting married in the winter. She also confirms they are getting married at the end of the year in this interview:

http://www.vegasmorningblend.com/videos/100168764.html

In the magazine article - sorry I can't find the link anymore - Vanessa said she wanted to start using Carmines name professionally. Which is fair enough, I just hope it is because she is very proud to be with him not to garner extra publicity of her return to GH.
